  "id": "RAW_c12d3570",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-4）：中兴开源 EmbodiedBrain1.0，使用 SFT+RL 双训练，突破具身智能对齐与实时性能瓶颈",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500723&idx=1&sn=dcf337fee2d29084d0052d374c0a8962",
  "date": "2025-12-04 09:32:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：EmbodiedBrain1.0&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5861111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"682\" data-imgfileid=\"100017062\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b722eb6b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw84Bqq0vrQxQ8cbtgLnrvEiaVIn5o3jicUDiaIUuZgBEYel8qUmJwVejjbibeMzdBBJFFTWbsSmiaJkeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EmbodiedBrain1.0 是一个先进的具身智能大脑模型，旨在解决当前具身 AI 模型在Agent对齐、实时性能和真实评估方面的挑战。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">模块化框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，用于训练和评估 7B 和 32B 视觉语言基础模型，支持大规模监督微调（SFT）和强化学习（RL）。其关键特性包括Agent对齐的数据结构、强大的 RL 训练方法（Step-GRPO）、灵活的奖励系统以及三部分评估基准。项目将开源所有数据、模型权重和评估方法，以推动通用具身Agent的研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/embodiedbrain1-0\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/embodiedbrain1-0</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Hermes 4.3</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"544\" data-imgfileid=\"100017061\" data-ratio=\"0.4666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=453d77ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw84Bqq0vrQxQ8cbtgLnrvEQcyhmRJvAz9pVe5ZLdC4wkMsXTrtpOS4xWKZF5Oe02Nqm3CNwx5Edg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Hermes 4.3 36B 是一个由 Nous Research 开发的前沿混合模式推理模型，基于 ByteDance Seed 36B 基础模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">互联网去中心化</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">训练，强调经过验证的推理轨迹，并在数学、代码、STEM、逻辑、创造力和格式忠实输出方面有显著提升，同时保持了通用助手的质量和中立性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hermes-4-3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hermes-4-3</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：STARFlow</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"516\" data-imgfileid=\"100017060\" data-ratio=\"0.44074074074074077\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e6a0058d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw84Bqq0vrQxQ8cbtgLnrvE3SARSBuSegLRV7ZWAPzGhkfiaG2oroMEj065mLVYedaeLooanAia4phw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★STARFlow是一个开源的自回归流模型，结合了自回归模型的表现力和正则化流的效率。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">文本生成图像</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视频任务</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">中实现了最先进的结果。STARFlow和STARFlow-V分别针对高分辨率图像合成和视频生成进行了优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/starflow\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/starflow</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：CUDA-L2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"206\" data-imgfileid=\"100017058\" data-ratio=\"0.17685185185185184\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e8dc6fae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw84Bqq0vrQxQ8cbtgLnrvEsickY0icCkYlJUTGO6jPA7hg7r00b74A8trvnDmicsS6VkC3o4UJ4Ghag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CUDA-L2 是一个结合大型语言模型（LLMs）和强化学习（RL）的系统，用于自动优化半精度通用矩阵乘法（HGEMM）的CUDA内核。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目在性能上系统性地超越了现有的主要矩阵乘法基准，包括广泛使用的torch.matmul和NVIDIA的闭源库（cuBLAS、cuBLASLt-heuristic、cuBLASLt-AutoTuning）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/cudal2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/cudal2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：ReCode</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"294\" data-imgfileid=\"100017059\" data-ratio=\"0.2518518518518518\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e472ad2e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw84Bqq0vrQxQ8cbtgLnrvE3ib4NOqApZEicE7YC7GaC8NFBp0gjxxbVQdj3x42RjxhyI2gAoadXSHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ReCode项目通过递归代码生成技术，将计划和行动统一为单一表示形式，旨在实现自适应和类人决策。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">分而治之</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的策略，将复杂任务分解为可执行的代码片段，并通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">树状结构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">组织部分程序。每个节点捕获一个子任务并记录其执行轨迹，使用环境特定的提示和少量示例进行递归扩展。项目提供了参考实现、环境包装器和实验工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/recode\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/recode</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：AN1 Meaning Engine</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"654\" data-imgfileid=\"100017063\" data-ratio=\"0.5611111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09105cb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw84Bqq0vrQxQ8cbtgLnrvEV060GgeKMRA0UCP7GdWuP7A9ah22JzorHNR8sng1OZ5SsUoqoxZiaaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AN1 Meaning Engine 是一个基于 PyTorch 的最小化演示项目，展示了如何通过提取矩阵前的语义来进行学习。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在证明冻结网络的早期层激活已经包含了最终语义意图的可用草图。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目使用冻结的 ResNet18 发送一个 64 维的头部，并通过一个小型 AN1 头部以超过 10 倍的推理速度和超过 1000 倍更少的 FLOPs 重建其行为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/an1-meaning-engine\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/an1-meaning-engine</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "汇总了中兴 EmbodiedBrain1.0 等多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖具身智能、LLM、代码生成及性能优化。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "汇总了中兴 EmbodiedBrain1.0 等多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖具身智能、LLM、代码生成及性能优化。",
  "summary": "本文精选并介绍了近期六个重要的开源人工智能项目。其中包括中兴的具身智能大脑模型 EmbodiedBrain1.0，该模型通过 SFT+RL 双训练，致力于解决具身 AI 在 Agent 对齐、实时性能和真实评估上的挑战。其他亮点项目包括 Nous Research 开发的混合模式推理模型 Hermes 4.3，其在数学、代码等领域表现出色；用于文本生成图像和视频的自回归流模型 STARFlow；结合 LLMs 和 RL 自动优化 CUDA 内核的 CUDA-L2 系统；通过递归代码生成实现自适应决策的 ReCode 项目；以及基于 PyTorch 高效提取语义的 AN1 Meaning Engine。文章为每个项目提供了简洁的功能描述和官方链接，旨在帮助技术从业者快速了解并探索最新的开源 AI 进展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "EmbodiedBrain1.0 旨在突破具身智能对齐与实时性能瓶颈",
      "explanation": "该项目提供模块化框架，通过 SFT+RL 双训练，解决具身 AI 在 Agent 对齐、实时性能和真实评估方面的核心挑战，并开源数据模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Hermes 4.3 显著提升了混合模式推理能力",
      "explanation": "基于 ByteDance Seed 36B 模型，通过去中心化训练，在数学、代码、STEM 等多个领域实现显著性能提升，同时保持通用助手质量。"
    },
